fields.raw_text:
[i]Introduction[/i]
This kit was issued in 2000 by Revell. Let's start by looking at the box-art, which gives an impression of the special paint version of the plane.

[b]Quality[/b]
Excellent details, crispy cast. Nice cockpit.

[b]Conclusion[/b]
One of the best kits there is of the Phantom II in 1/72!
